{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_28","type":"agent_message","text":"### Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed, but the evidence suggests the library compatibility issue itself was identified and the run most likely failed during preservation/reporting rather than during the final test execution.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-5598-fails-javac-compile-org.apache.camel-spi-annotations-4.0.0-5859fc24\n\nThe first blocking stage was `:compileTestJava`: `tests/src/org.apache.camel/spi-annotations/4.0.0/src/test/java/org_apache_camel/spi_annotations/Spi_annotationsTest.java` still referenced `UriEndpoint.label()` and `label = \"testing,core\"`, which are not present in Camel 4.0.0. See `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:spi-annotations:4.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T01-51-00-596441Z.log`.\n\nThe concrete fix appears in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:spi-annotations:4.0.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-05T01-51-38-475659Z.log`: replace `label` usage with `UriEndpoint.category()`, add `org.apache.camel.Category`, and change the annotation value to `category = {Category.TESTING, Category.CORE}`. After that change, both later Gradle reruns succeeded with 10/10 tests passing and `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`; see `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:spi-annotations:4.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T01-53-03-450834Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:spi-annotations:4.0.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T01-53-36-060197Z.log`.\n\nThe mismatch is that `stats/org.apache.camel/spi-annotations/4.0.0/execution-metrics.json` still reports `status: failure`, `iterations: 1`, `generated_loc: 0`, and `artifacts.test_file: None`, and the preserved branch does not keep the restored `tests/src/org.apache.camel/spi-annotations/4.0.0/...` files.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Reapply the test change captured in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.camel:spi-annotations:4.0.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-05T01-51-38-475659Z.log` to `tests/src/org.apache.camel/spi-annotations/4.0.0/src/test/java/org_apache_camel/spi_annotations/Spi_annotationsTest.java`.\n2. Restore the deleted `tests/src/org.apache.camel/spi-annotations/4.0.0` test project files on a follow-up branch/commit.\n3. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.camel:spi-annotations:4.0.0` to confirm the preserved fix is actually recorded."}}
